{"tid":42771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉露械老翁稱小便女童：狗先得","createTime":"2016-12-17T03:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T06:24:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c6f4e4810c65e77015a95f3dc54f71c5565409","tid":42771,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:53:35.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】育有一對5歲孖女的婦人帶孖女到公園玩耍，卻只顧打電話，以致有年近九旬老翁三度向孖女露械，她仍懵然不知，結果要細孖通知，再由女街坊報警將老翁拘捕。 <br />\n<br />\n警方調查後發現，老翁涉在幾日前非禮另一名5歲女童。案件昨在粉嶺法院開審，辯方指老翁當時並非露械，只是小解，孖女不同意辯方說法，細孖更直言「唔可以咁，狗先得！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n89歲被告王華堯否認一項非禮及三項向16歲以下兒童作猥褻行為罪，3名事主X、Y及Z透過視像系統作供，Y、Z是孖女。X供稱今年8月3日在天水圍一個公園玩耍時，被告吻她的嘴及緊捉她的手摸其陽具。 <br />\nY及Z同月6日到同一個公園玩耍。赤裸上身的王兩度招手着Y上前，然後掏出陽具輕輕地搖，再着Z上前並露械，Z通知身處公園的母親。下周一續審。 <br />\n<br />\n案件編號：FLCC3894/16 <br />\n■記者戴國輝 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161217/19868138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161217%2F19868138&d=Bt8vY%2FcGdb2BO3jI8rmSWJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=cfdb4a94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161217%2F19868138&h=fcd719cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161217/19868138</a>"},{"pid":"cc34911f004473af7a6fceef299f569ec933b774","tid":42771,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:55:25.000Z","msg":"廢老連細路都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714c052675a565d645bb2a010eef569e87480721","tid":42771,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"靚妹都呃唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8f6ba62aac6c26f49adbe93bad2a2d9fa74eb8","tid":42771,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:59:30.000Z","msg":"個妹妹講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.